{"tid":2145162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美媒斥《南早》改稿撐警","createTime":"2020-08-08T02:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T02:11:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f20670ee67dab96421be97249851e605cd826f32","tid":2145162,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:11:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200808/CWBPMCYNP2EACD6C3EB3ZWN4QE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200808%2FCWBPMCYNP2EACD6C3EB3ZWN4QE%2F&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=29443ea5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200808%2FCWBPMCYNP2EACD6C3EB3ZWN4QE%2F&h=56d829a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200808/CWBPMCYNP2EACD6C3EB3ZWN4QE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美媒斥《南早》改稿撐警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Uhgy6llREMxpMzudG9IdlrwZTBY=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MC4CBEXPRUPX2BEWKURM6ROESM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUhgy6llREMxpMzudG9IdlrwZTBY%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMC4CBEXPRUPX2BEWKURM6ROESM.jpg&h=a6b7f264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《南華早報》被美國傳媒批評，有編輯屢更改記者的稿件，加入「暴亂」等字眼。資料圖片&lt;br /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港銷量最高的英文收費報紙《南華早報》 4年前被中資阿里巴巴收購後，一直被質疑「染紅」。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n指多名記者離職<br />\n<br />\n《大西洋》雜誌8月1日刊出題為〈專制邊緣的編輯室〉文章，談及《南早》變化，並以8.31事件報道為例，指《南早》記者原稿為「現場混亂及令人震驚，警察衝向驚慌的乘客」，但刊出版本被改成「精英香港警察（elite Hong Kong police）」追捕「激進示威者（radical protesters）」，批評報道內容偏頗。文章又指隨着社會運動事態發展，已有一些負責相關報道的記者選擇離職。<br />\n<br />\n文章又訪問多名《南早》記者，引述指不少記者不滿新聞報道偏幫香港警察。其中多名記者矛頭指向《南早》首席新聞編輯雲丹‧拉圖（Yonden Lhatoo），批評他多次撰寫與示威相關的偏頗報道及社論。"}]}